cy admission test.\nHe was immediately accepted into the field of general surgery and completed his degree with a nationally-honored degree and was selected as a faculty member.\nSubsequently, he was accepted to the specialty exam in Plastic, Reconstructive and Aesthetic Surgery and after a three-year specialization in this field, he graduated from Shahid Beheshti University of Medical Sciences.\nCurrently, he is an Exemplary Professor at Iran University of Medical Sciences.\nHe has had several surgeries so far and has had numerous international and domestic articles and has authored numerous books.\nSo far, he has been elected to the University three times as an Exemplary Professor and is currently working in the field of medical education as a consultant with the Deputy Minister of Education of the Ministry of Health and Medical Education.\nIt should be noted that he is a member of the Society of Specialist Plastic Surgeons of the country\n- Editorial Board of the top scientific and research journals of the country\n- The jury member of international journals of plastic, reconstructive and cosmetic surgeons.','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-02-14 10:00:00','2019-10-30 06:09:57','doctors/October2019/BIZBuMyaqEXrF1lgywpJ.jpg','[\"doctors\\/October2019\\/gfzCTAuwJhMvQSziibNM.jpg\",\"doctors\\/October2019\\/7arSYUfIensUeGJZhQqD.jpg\"]',1,'aldktwr-hmydrdha-alyzadh-ataqwr',100,'{\n    \"1\": {\n        \"name\": \"Shahid Beheshti University of Medical Sciences\",\n        \"degree\": \"Specialty in Plastic, Reconstructive and Cosmetic Surgery\",\n        \"date\": \"1988\"\n       }\n}\n','{\n    \"1\": {\n        \"skill\": \"Rhinoplasty\",\n        \"percent\": \"100\"\n    },\n\"2\": {\n        \"skill\": \"Otoplasty (Ear surgery)\",\n        \"percent\": \"95\"\n    },\n\"3\": {\n        \"skill\": \"Blepharoplasty (Eyelid Surgery)\",\n        \"percent\": \"90\"\n    },\n\"4\": {\n        \"skill\": \"Face lift\",\n        \"percent\": \"90\"\n    },\n   \"5\": {\n     