INSERT INTO `faqs` VALUES (1,'What is Medtouriran?','<p>Medtouriran is an online medical tourism facilitator platform to provide this opportunity for citizens of one country to travel to IRAN and obtain high quality and affordable health care services. At now, this platform is active in Tehran, Mashhad and Shiraz, the biggest cities in Iran. Medtouriran provides all services international patients need include visa, flight, transfer, accommodation, medical and cosmetic services, city sightseeing and follow up.</p>',NULL,'2019-08-15 00:05:00','2019-08-31 10:14:55',1),(2,'Which medical and cosmetic services are provided in Medtouriran?','<p>The various elective medical services include diagnostic, ENT (ear, nose and throat), orthopedic, eye care, infertility, cardiology, dental health, and cosmetic operation include rhinoplasty, hair transplant, tommy tuck, liposuction, mammoplasty, eyelids surgery and so on are provided in Medtouriran.<span style=\"color: #00ffff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #00ffff;\" href=\"https://medtouriran.com/en/procedures\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> Click here</a></strong></span> to view the list of our procedures and<span style=\"color: #00ffff;\"> <strong><a style=\"color: #00ffff;\" href=\"https://medtouriran.com/en/packages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">click here</a></strong></span> to view our medical and cosmetic packages. We also provide complementary and alternative medicine treatment for various diseased conditions that you can fill out our contact form at the bottom of the page if you need.</p>',NULL,'2019-08-15 00:05:00','2019-08-31 10:16:44',1),(3,'What should I do if the treatment I’m looking for is not mentioned in your platform?','<p>We have mentioned only some common popular treatments and cosmetic services in our website. If the treatment you are looking for is not undertaken at our platform, we are here to guide you for selection of the best possible options according to your requirement and medical condition. You can fill out our contact form and our colleague let you know more about various other medical and cosmetic procedures.</p>',NULL,'2019-08-31 09:18:00','2019-09-02 00:13:46',1),(4,' In which criteria medical centers (clinics and hospitals) are selected? ','<p>We thrive on providing affordable and excellent medical services. We have chosen our affiliation on the basis of below mentioned criteria.</p>\n<p> State of art infrastructure</p>\n<p> Use of latest technology</p>\n<p> Well experienced health care provider</p>\n<p> Latest pathology and diagnostic laboratory</p>\n<p> Supportive cooperative staff, who can understand English and Arabic languages.</p>\n<p> Excellent hospitality</p>\n<p> Back-up plans and facilities to counter emergency needs - electrical power back up, enough competitive staff, blood arrangement, ambulance, escorts facility</p>\n<p> Cleanliness and hygienic environment</p>\n<p> Proper location- easy to reach destination that has easy access to other facilities such as market. Located at a quiet place away from noise and pollution of traffic.</p>\n<p> Review of their international, domestic, clinical and service credentials.</p>\n<p> We visit the place personally time to time and are in constant connection with organization, their staff to have the latest updates.</p>',NULL,'2019-08-31 09:19:00','2019-08-31 10:08:08',1),(5,'Which preparation is needed before a medical treatment travel?','<p>There are certain &lsquo;must know&rsquo; parameters which need to be carefully evaluated to ensure successful outcome and stay away from disastrous medical travel. The guidelines that will help you to have successful and fruitful medical journey are as mentioned below:</p>\n<p> Selection of the destination</p>\n<p> Selection of medical center, clinic or doctor. We let you know the educational, back-ground, work experience, patient&rsquo;s testimonials and success ratio of the concerned surgeon through clicking <span style=\"color: #00ffff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #00ffff;\" href=\"https://medtouriran.com/en/services/doctors\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">our doctors</a>. </strong></span></p>\n<p> Consult with our wellness experts.</p>\n<p> To make sure you have a signed and valid passport and the required visa. It is better to have some copies of passport identification page that will be of great help if the passport is lost or stolen.</p>\n<p> To keep the scanned or photo copies of passport, passport photos, medical records, and paper tickets with the list of important phone numbers in email accounts.</p>\n<p> To carry complete medical reports/doctors notes, as well as copy of all drug prescriptions.<span style=\"color: #00ffff;\"> <strong><a style=\"color: #00ffff;\" href=\"https://medtouriran.com/en/blogs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Read more</a></strong></span></p>',NULL,'2019-08-31 09:19:00','2019-08-31 10:16:14',1);
