INSERT INTO `hotels` VALUES (1,'Espinas Palace Hotel',5,1,'\0\0\0\0\0\0\0+','<p class=\"paragraph-medium paragraph-black text-left\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #777777;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Espanas Palace stare its looks with its location in the northern region of Tehran, like the hidden jewel in a quiet paradise. This hotel offers a variety of luxury services, with different expectations. Also, the design of this hotel, using contemporary architecture and impressed by the amazing architecture of the past, has considered the tastes of all ages. Perhaps this is why the name has been chosen as \"Palace\". Additionally, this eye-catching palace is one of the finest in Tehran, with a magnificent lobby, spectacular public spaces, and especially standard equipped rooms. All of the expectations of a five-star hotel are best suited for this hotel. This feature has made all the guests experience a comfortable stay. We will be deeply happy to be happy with your warm presence at Spinas Palas.</span></p>',3,2,85,'hotels/July2019/iTpSBDPg2ryI7Jr3MYQU.jpg','[\"hotels\\/July2019\\/iB8EOFAyqC94qgyNPfua.jpg\",\"hotels\\/July2019\\/JUBHkcT0DAdYsA43IoFz.jpg\",\"hotels\\/July2019\\/HZ17pYFtsi5VMeamAFIu.jpg\",\"hotels\\/July2019\\/UDGDupxzxj7ESxs7eRvg.jpg\"]','2019-07-01 10:11:00','2019-09-08 12:48:07','Espinas Palace Hotel','hotels',25,'hotels/September2019/Row64W5I64gtD9cxPj2R.jpg'),(2,'Hotel Parsian Kosar',4,1,'\0\0\0\0\0\0\0+','<p>Parsian Kosar Hotel is a beautiful residence of the Parsian Hotel Group in Tehran. This hotel is located near the city market and offers good access to the Carpet Museum, Golestan Palace, Sa\'ad Abad and Niavaran. The interior of the hotel is designed by traditional Iranian architecture with mirror and beautiful paintings. In the restaurant of this hotel, delicious Persian and French cuisine are cooked, which is one of the most remarkable prominences in the hotel. Parsian Kosar Hotel is a traditional tablecloth with delightful atmosphere along with authentic Persian dishes for travelers.</p>',NULL,3,50,'hotels/July2019/7RoQSoVgKFGZRw0Q4J4V.jpg','[\"hotels\\/July2019\\/8bvi5f1KMKoUmlNRic5t.jpg\",\"hotels\\/July2019\\/PinPPeuXbuuu2om74c6u.jpg\",\"hotels\\/July2019\\/LSBcerS4fjxA4o9Fmoda.jpg\"]','2019-07-27 02:55:00','2019-08-13 03:11:43','fndq-bars-an-wthr','hotels',24,NULL),(3,'Hotel Parsian Azadi',5,1,'\0\0\0\0\0\0\0+','<p>Parsian Azadi Hotel Tehran is one of the best 5 star hotels in Tehran. Located next to the mountain range of Alborz Mountains, this hotel is located in a peaceful spot in the immediate vicinity of the international exhibition hall of the summit.</p>\n<p>Although the Parsian Azadi Hotel is far from the city center, it is accessible to all parts of the city, including attractions and places of interest, at the crossing of main roads. From the Parsian Azadi Hotel, you can easily go to Zurastic Park and Saadabad Beach Resort and Resort Mountain.</p>\n<p>In the Parsian Hotel, Tehran has everything to offer a comfortable and relaxing stay. The most appealing restaurants, the most equipped meeting rooms and the best rooms and suites.</p>',3,3,78,'hotels/July2019/xDzyUL2vIMsCEONU0nEd.jpg','[\"hotels\\/July2019\\/Sn6WCz2EZm665PaBXVpJ.jpg\",\"hotels\\/July2019\\/KHFMQ3ZwXCRTWUYJoa3m.jpg\"]','2019-07-27 03:10:00','2019-08-13 03:11:43','fndq-bars-an-aazad','hotels',23,NULL),(5,'Sasan Hotel ',2,1,'\0\0\0\0\0\0\0+','<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><em><strong>Sasan Hotel</strong></em></span> is a 2-star hotel located in Tehran and is close to shopping, medical and center of Tehran. Dear travelers and tourists can enjoy this privilege of traveling around Tehran without worrying about staying at this hotel. Hotel Sasan has a short drive to Hafte Tir Square which is easily accessible to other areas such as Sepah Square, Mofateh Street, 