ص های مرتبط با بیماری های چشم، با مرکز چشم بصیر شیراز همکاری می نماید.</span></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'hotels/August2019/GP0iuhjshDrht4MeajvA.jpeg',NULL,'2019-08-03 06:41:00','2019-11-18 06:55:02','basir-shiraz-eye-center','medical-centers',12,NULL),(16,'Parsian Esteghlal Hotel',5,1,'\0\0\0\0\0\0\0+','<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><em><strong>Parsian Esteghlal Hotel</strong></em></span> Located in north of Tehran, is an ideal choice for those traveling to the capital of Iran.Situated in one of the best parts of Tehran, Parsian Esteghlal hotel&nbsp; has convenient access to the longest street in the Middle-East and the most beautiful street in the Tehran(Valiasr Street). This Hotel is also close to Tehran International Exhibition, Milad Tower, Resort Television, and shopping and sightseeing areas of the city. Four national restaurants (French, Italian, Thai, Arabic) will make you the most delicious food in the faraway lands without having to go there.Young personnel and Fluency in hotel principles are another benefits of this hotel.</p>',NULL,NULL,35,'hotels/August2019/FZbrRM5ND603UX0B7sNt.jpg','[\"hotels\\/August2019\\/yAAJRzsgWolv1MlqqCfd.jpg\",\"hotels\\/August2019\\/Y2gidmhyAWNXBKZzqmuX.jpg\",\"hotels\\/August2019\\/6Xf69BvDiKNZwJ8RoOZs.jpg\",\"hotels\\/August2019\\/iHZI1gOnGhzSOUHgCkr1.jpg\"]','2019-08-03 06:44:00','2019-08-29 08:33:03','parsian-esteghlal-hotel','hotels',11,NULL),(17,'Zandieh Hotel',5,3,'\0\0\0\0\0\0\0+','<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><em><strong>Shiraz Zandieh Hotel</strong></em></span> is one of the most stylish and luxurious hotels in Shiraz.An overnight stay at this hotel will make you a permanent fan of it.The hotel has a traditional bathroom, pool, sauna and Jacuzzi. A variety of restaurants with a variety of delectable dishes is another advantage of this 5-star hotel. The traditional restaurant is one of them with a special atmosphere and authentic cuisine. High speed internet and travel agencies are also some of the benefits 