ohammad Nasir Naderi graduated from the University of Tehran with a degree in General Medicine in 2007. After completing his military service, he began his residency course in orthopedics at the University of Iran, and began his career as an orthopedic specialist in bone and joint surgery. After graduating, he also gained valuable experience by continuing to work with trainees in the field of trauma, particularly intra-articular fracture problems and hip fractures.\nFor a subspecialty, he completed a 6-month course in Arthroscopy & Sport Traumatology in Austria and had  a 5-month training in shoulder and arthroscopic course under the supervision of Professor Funk spent in England.','2019-10-30 07:13:09','2019-10-30 07:13:09'),(947,'doctors','education',24,'ar','{\n    \"1\": {\n        \"name\": \"جامعة طهران للعلوم الطبية\",\n        \"degree\": \"الطب العام\",\n        \"date\": \"1997\"\n    },\n    \"2\": {\n        \"name\": \"مجلس العظام التخصصي\",\n        \"degree\": \"جامعة إيران للعلوم الطبية \",\n        \"date\": \"2003\"\n     },\n    \"3\": {\n        \"name\": \"جراحة الكتف والكوع وتنظير المفصل\",\n        \"degree\": \"إنجلترا (مستشفى جامعة ليفربول الملكي)\",\n        \"date\": \"2007\"\n}\n}\n','2019-10-30 07:13:09','2019-10-30 07:13:09'),(948,'doctors','education',24,'ku','{\n    \"1\": {\n        \"name\": \"University of Tehran\",\n        \"degree\": \"General Medicine\",\n        \"date\": \"2007\"\n    },\n    \"2\": {\n        \"name\": \"residency course in orthopedicss\",\n        \"degree\": \"University of Iran \",\n        \"date\": \"2010\"\n     },\n    \"3\": {\n        \"name\": \"shoulder and arthroscopic course\",\n        \"degree\": \"England (under the supervision of Professor Funk) \",\n        \"date\": \"2013\"\n}\n}\n','2019-10-30 07:13:09','2019-10-30 07:13:09'),(949,'doctors','skills',24,'ar','\n{\n    \"1\": {\n        \"skill\": \"جراحة الكتف بالمنظار\",\n        \"percent\": \"100\"\n    },\n\"2\": {\n        \"skill\":